# Component Patterns

## Page structure

- Each page is a default export in `src/pages/`.
- Pages compose sections as JSX — no separate section components unless reused across pages.
- Admin pages live in `src/pages/admin/` and use `adminApi` from `src/lib/adminApi.ts`.

## Styling

- Use Tailwind utility classes exclusively.
- Custom theme tokens: `bg-bg-primary`, `bg-bg-secondary`, `bg-bg-card`, `text-text-primary`, `text-text-secondary`, `border-border`, `text-green-brand`, `text-green-accent`, `bg-green-brand`, `bg-green-accent`.
- Dark backgrounds for public pages, white cards for product cards and forms.
- Responsive: use `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:` breakpoints. Mobile-first.

## Forms

- Controlled inputs with `useState`.
- Status pattern: `"idle" | "sending" | "sent" | "error"`.
- Extract reusable `Field` components per page (not globally shared — each page may style differently).

## Data fetching

- Use `useEffect` + `useState` for fetching. No external data-fetching library.
- Public API: `api.get/post/put/delete` from `src/lib/api.ts`.
- Admin API: `adminApi.get/post/put/patch/delete/upload` from `src/lib/adminApi.ts`.
- Handle loading and error states in each page.

## Icons

- Use `lucide-react` for all icons. Import individually: `import { IconName } from "lucide-react"`.
